detail.name: Currency One USD
detail.public_notice: USD1 (USD1) has been rebranded to Currency One USD (C1USD). They migrated from their old contract to a new contract. For more information, please visit this post and visit the old token page here.

description.en: Currency One USD (C1USD) is a USD-pegged stablecoin issued by Kinesis Money Panama S.A. (“Kinesis Panama”). Every C1USD is backed by a 1:1 asset reserve. Kinesis Money Panama S.A. is the entity responsible for its issuance and management within the Kinesis ecosystem. C1USD is the first asset in the Currency One Suite of single-currency stablecoins.
